      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Conferences\" title=\"Conferences\">Conferences</a> * Advances in Computer Games 14</b>\n</p><p><b><a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_13\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 13\">&lt; Prev</a> <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_15\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 15\">Next &gt;</a></b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:SnelliusBuilding_2015.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/de/SnelliusBuilding_2015.JPG/300px-SnelliusBuilding_2015.JPG\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/d/de/SnelliusBuilding_2015.JPG 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:SnelliusBuilding_2015.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Snellius Building <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Advances in Computer Games 14</b>,<br />\nfrom July 1 to 3, <a href=\"/Timeline#2015\" title=\"Timeline\">2015</a>, Snellius Building <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, <a href=\"/Leiden_University\" title=\"Leiden University\">Leiden University</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leiden\">Leiden</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Netherlands\">The Netherlands</a>, in conjunction with the <a href=\"/WCCC_2015\" title=\"WCCC 2015\">WCCC 2015</a>, <a href=\"/WCSC_2015\" title=\"WCSC 2015\">WCSC 2015</a>, and the <a href=\"/18th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"18th Computer Olympiad\">18th Computer Olympiad</a>. ACG is the conference of the <a href=\"/ICGA\" title=\"ICGA\">ICGA</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" c